item.title: A new website
item.description: This website is largely thanks to Max Dima and Andrei. The Artwork Max Dima made all the artwork, his Illustrator skills are quite remarkable. He is responsible for websites like https://online.io and a few others that are in the making. His behance profile is also something to behold. The Code Andrei is responsible for the website it self. He is the CTO of Engage and works as a fullstack developer at Around25.
